@startuml KnowledgeArchitecture
\!theme plain

package "Knowledge Layer" {
  [shared-memory.json] as KB
  [MCP Memory Server] as MCP
  [VKB Visualization] as VKB
}

package "Capture Tools" {
  [UKB Auto Mode] as Auto
  [UKB Interactive] as Interactive
  [UKB Agent Mode] as Agent
}

package "Development" {
  [Git Repository] as Git
  [Code Files] as Code
  [Conversation Logs] as Logs
}

Git --> Auto : Commit analysis
Logs --> Auto : Session insights
Code --> Agent : Semantic analysis
Interactive --> KB : Manual insights

Auto --> KB : Patterns & insights
Agent --> KB : Deep analysis
Interactive --> KB : Structured knowledge

KB <--> MCP : Runtime sync
KB --> VKB : Visualization
MCP --> "Development Session" : Pattern guidance

@enduml
EOF < /dev/null